# Student Leave Management System (Java Console Project)

A simple console-based Java application that helps manage student leave requests. The system allows students to apply for leave and enables an admin to review, approve, or reject those applications.

## Features

- Student leave application
- Admin review and status update
- Persistent storage using text files
- Menu-driven console interface
- Basic object-oriented design using Java

## Technologies Used

- Java (OOP, File I/O, Collections)
- Text file for data storage (No external database)


